our own heads; I am clean: from henceforth I will go unto the Gentiles.","year":54},{"id":"recudEiT6O2w5HJKm","ref":"Acts.18.7","text":"And he departed thence, and entered into a certain man’s house, named Justus, one that worshipped God, whose house joined hard to the synagogue.","year":54},{"id":"recgN9Cj2gXmgw5Pu","ref":"Acts.18.8","text":"And Crispus, the chief ruler of the synagogue, believed on the Lord with all his house; and many of the Corinthians hearing believed, and were baptized.","year":54}]}
